Package: bulkATACquality
Type: Package
Title: Predict quality of human post-mortem brain bulk ATAC-seq sample 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jingyu Zhang
Maintainer: Jingyu Zhang <whale5879@gmail.com>
Description: Generate quality metrics plots and related statistics to predict quality of sample.
    All plots and tables can be generated if input a BAM file, 
    an HTML file of prediction result, statistics, and plots can also be generated.  
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
